{"tid":853554,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[不定期後補]9月尾去完Banff, 少少分享","createTime":"2018-10-08T16:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T05:19:49.000Z","uid":101799,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"688e4c03ec2b8773aea6b465e727f37432e8b17a","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"個行程由溫哥華出發，租車9日<br />\n一般人都會玩埋Jasper，不過我就臨時改行程只玩Banff (冇左成千蚊deposit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n主要原因係出發前睇左 Paul Zizka&rsquo;s Guide to Photography in the Canadian Rockies，又冇認真 plan 行程。所以就決定跟住介紹慢遊 Banff...<br />\n<br />\n首先介紹既係Vermilion lakes，呢張係零晨五點左右曝45分鐘左右。後來天光所以冇得再疊相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1974/44237736445_f4a3c31aaf_k_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1974%2F44237736445_f4a3c31aaf_k_d.jpg&h=3b6e598b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(如果張圖太大，話聲我知，會改返細張)<br />\n<br />\n一共三大個湖既 Vermilion lakes 應該係最易去既湖。由Banff 揸車不到十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 影相位都係馬路五分鐘路程。隨時上返車保暖又得。好幾個位都可以有好多角度。<br />\n<br />\n不過日落時份都幾多人去，都係朝早少人比較好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de505539378f1fdc2796e26a470074c38616172","tid":853554,"uid":150110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"點解會放棄jasper既，純粹想花多d時間係banff影靚相？"},{"pid":"68e743d44166dff5aa1fdfa84d5b3ad6e6307397","tid":853554,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5633dd56d82439c45b014418a2907fc04758405e","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1de505539378f1fdc2796e26a470074c38616172","tid":853554,"uid":150110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"點解會放棄jasper既，純粹想花多d時間係banff影靚相？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"睇過相，感覺冇Banff 咁靚。另一個原因係想減少揸車時間，留多d時間玩。<br />\n<br />\n以前試過六日揸二千公里，雖然揸車好玩，不過都唔想太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fe59bb45b80c8fbcd7466bfcfa78d24d43bd2d","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"繼續 Vermilion Lakes<br />\n三個湖都有個小碼頭，應該玩水上活動用。亦可自拍chok 相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於中秋過後果日，月光仲係好圓。整個風景係零晨五點都仲清楚可見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1974/44427787724_50c34e05ae_k_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1974%2F44427787724_50c34e05ae_k_d.jpg&h=563bc7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於日出，不過好平凡。可以提早返酒店食早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1909/44427788304_fe51573766_k_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1909%2F44427788304_fe51573766_k_d.jpg&h=d31b51ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於交通太方便，隔一日又返來影日落。本來個天好多雲，但突然出現紅霞。影日出日落真係好估你唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1911/44427782814_2aae78e816_k_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1911%2F44427782814_2aae78e816_k_d.jpg&h=4269e6f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2d54721bcb0e7b4c13b2ccbcbdd2749f7528791","tid":853554,"uid":150110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5633dd56d82439c45b014418a2907fc04758405e","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1de505539378f1fdc2796e26a470074c38616172","tid":853554,"uid":150110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"點解會放棄jasper既，純粹想花多d時間係banff影靚相？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"睇過相，感覺冇Banff 咁靚。另一個原因係想減少揸車時間，留多d時間玩。<br />\n<br />\n以前試過六日揸二千公里，雖然揸車好玩，不過都唔想太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:15:53.000Z","msg":"冇banff咁靚同唔洗揸咁耐車就真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩6月同屋企去曬兩度，淨係得我呀爸揸車勁辛苦。<br />\n但我覺得兩邊賣點唔同，jasper比較local同偏向wildlife個邊，如果有機會我都覺得可以去下睇下加拿大人點樣manage個國家公園，帶遊客去睇wildlife 同時亦會尊重佢地！<br />\nBtw d相好靚！"},{"pid":"49723a64a73644e3205ee071766ec9e5c3c7666c","tid":853554,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"咁岩我又係舊年9月尾去Banff<br />\n又係冇去Jasper，有d後悔，因為Jasper瑪琳湖都幾靚同幾出名<br />\n不過我係溫哥華跟local tour去"},{"pid":"9dadb160c82488b29afbe6e9b8eef227227b3c07","tid":853554,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"D相好靚係咪落哂FILTER影?"},{"pid":"3501a8fbd479a416ae1a59430d74fe8b6b7bad70","tid":853554,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"banff 咩月份去最靚？<br />\n有冇行程推介？<br />\n下年畢業諗緊好唔好去vancouver 玩2星期會唔會太多？ vancouver --&gt; calgary --&gt; Edmonton"},{"pid":"e346259ddb15367223836cd2d1526b087ef118f8","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"下一個要介紹既係 Two Jack Lake<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1945/44427788784_a0e9961e30_k_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1945%2F44427788784_a0e9961e30_k_d.jpg&h=f9edf816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係Banff 十幾分鐘車程，有上下兩個停車場。當然停下面停車場就方便，落車就已經係湖邊。北面有個小山丘可以高位取景。往南行就有個湖心島，不過會擋到雪山。太近影會影到樹高過坐雪山，感覺唔良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上圖就係湖心湖向東北影，背景係比較普通一座山。不過有晚霞襯托都唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n下圖就向南影返雪山，日落後四十五分鐘時影的。天差不太全黑，靠30秘長曝光同PS推對比。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1951/44427789094_924a5ddd04_k_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1951%2F44427789094_924a5ddd04_k_d.jpg&h=52bddcf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n書仔話呢個湖無乜風，如果Vermilion Lakes 大風可以上來呢度影。但我既經驗係相反。吹到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果日個湖邊有班人玩，所以都唔驚俾熊食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57883759e267d91f360af8684c6afbebdca7192a","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dadb160c82488b29afbe6e9b8eef227227b3c07","tid":853554,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"D相好靚係咪落哂FILTER影?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"只落ND, 後悔冇買到最黑果隻。所以有時曝得唔夠耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f42c2986f2ebeaef5d2d0d2e8c07f4e785b6f2","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3501a8fbd479a416ae1a59430d74fe8b6b7bad70","tid":853554,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"banff 咩月份去最靚？<br />\n有冇行程推介？<br />\n下年畢業諗緊好唔好去vancouver 玩2星期會唔會太多？ vancouver --&gt; calgary --&gt; Edmonton"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"每個季節都有唔同景色，但要留意開放時間。<br />\n我自己鐘意睇雪，希望將來冬季會去。<br />\nbtw, 冬天部份地方會封路，纜車都有開放時間。最全計劃時睇定先，唔好好似我咁，去到摸門釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，旺季住都幾貴。淡季比可以平25～50%。。。"},{"pid":"784b46d3e4641d54f3af4dffb5ebacdffd8a4525","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"Johnson Lake 係 Two Jake Lake 附近(開車既話)， 但游人就比較少。天書話可以環湖一周。但一丁友，四下無人實在有點淆底。都係開揚地方影下算。<br />\n<br />\n果日天陰陰，都估到冇咩機會。但一場來到就搏下拉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1980/44427783634_62a93075b4_k_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1980%2F44427783634_62a93075b4_k_d.jpg&h=38ed4e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n風起雲湧，第二日就落雨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n取景不及Two Jack Lake 咁好，或者我搵唔到好位。"},{"pid":"53c2b727352a1599612f90c81e27c306960386a8","tid":853554,"uid":150110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f42c2986f2ebeaef5d2d0d2e8c07f4e785b6f2","tid":853554,"uid":101799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3501a8fbd479a416ae1a59430d74fe8b6b7bad70","tid":853554,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"banff 咩月份去最靚？<br />\n有冇行程推介？<br />\n下年畢業諗緊好唔好去vancouver 玩2星期會唔會太多？ vancouver --&gt; calgary --&gt; Edmonton"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"每個季節都有唔同景色，但要留意開放時間。<br />\n我自己鐘意睇雪，希望將來冬季會去。<br />\nbtw, 冬天部份地方會封路，纜車都有開放時間。最全計劃時睇定先，唔好好似我咁，去到摸門釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，旺季住都幾貴。淡季比可以平25～50%。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:16:27.000Z","msg":"比你做個參考，我岩岩6月頭去既，應該都叫做開始旺季，但唔知係咪始終都仲有少少凍，我覺得人未算好多。<br />\n天氣就唔算好好，但都唔算好差，keep住間中都落毛毛雨咁。<br />\n上左去lake louise gondola，上到去上面係落緊雪既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩有著羽絨上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/091358_f78cf8db87aae460fc8f59b988f85405.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F091358_f78cf8db87aae460fc8f59b988f85405.png&h=584f948b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/091401_0c207d6225ced9635c9228dcd150bf90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F091401_0c207d6225ced9635c9228dcd150bf90.png&h=e32e06ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩張相只係隔左幾分鐘影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你係打算vancouver 一直自己揸車咁玩到edmonton?<br />\n會唔會去埋jasper?<br />\n我6月沿路去jasper個陣愈上愈高就愈多地方落緊雪，好靚"},{"pid":"ed92a188fecd3fd4f85ef9cf5f9c4187fa1180eb","tid":853554,"uid":150807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇用ND?<br />\n有既話又係用幾級?<br />\n感謝"},{"pid":"1f5fe8cb8a4474a67672515573188018ed9a91ec","tid":853554,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}